parse-statement
SELECT foo
FROM bar+1 ORDER
BY
----
error: Expected end of statement, found operator "+"
FROM bar+1 ORDER
        ^

parse-statement
SELECT * FROM db.public..customer
----
error: Expected identifier, found dot
SELECT * FROM db.public..customer
                        ^

